==== Sharing====
[[File:SharingPedestal.webp|thumb|200x200px|A sharing pedestal with a palette]]
[[Special:MyLanguage/Sharing|Sharing]] enables a VRC+ user to share custom emojis, custom stickers, photos, prints, and UI themes with other users. This allows a user to place a Sharing Pedestal in a world that other users can interact with. When a user leaves an instance, their pedestal will disappear. Sharing pedestals can be hidden by selecting it, blocking a user will also hide their pedestal.